        <description>Guide customers through the refund request procedures, including initiating the process automatically when a product is reported as damaged or unsatisfactory.</description>
        <developerName>Refund_Process_16jg8000000TLIn</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If a customer expresses the desire to return a product, request the order number and product name and create a Refund Request record and inform the customer of the Refund Request details and that a customer service agent will review the request.</description>
